        Enterprise API Architect
        At ADP our data and APIs play a critical role in our overall architecture. We are looking for a smart, experienced and self-motivated API Architect to join ADP's Enterprise Architecture team. In this capacity, you will work with the Domain Data Stewards to standardization and design APIs within and across the HCM business domains. You will work with data and API subject matter experts (SMEs), Architect/Engineers, Product Managers, API Stewards, App developers, and Back-end Engineers/Architects to help deliver a broad suite of ADP's APIs.
        We strive for every interaction to be driven by our CORE values: Insightful Expertise, Integrity is Everything, Service Excellence, Inspiring Innovation, Each Person Counts, Results-Driven, & Social Responsibility.
